{
  "stem": "3605.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we talked to each other that, by the first opportunity, we are going to try to run away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we passed the forest, and Hanka ran a way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there I was left without her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then when we passed another forest, we-- I ran away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But little did I know, it wasn't a forest.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was just a triangle of trees.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there I ran in into some Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they took me by my collar, and they schlepped me back to the transport.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I thought that, by God, I am going to be shot just this time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But evidently, I was meant to live to be able to tell my story.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the German just gave me a few hard kicks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I joined in to the working transport.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "When the evening came close, they put all the prisoners into a barn, a few barns, and locked the doors.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I don't know what power possessed me and three other girls.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We lifted out the barn door from the hinges.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The Germans were evidently at the farmer's house having a good time there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I and three other girls ran away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The other people didn't even want to run.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They didn't know where to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They were afraid, because the Americans were shooting from one side.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And the Germans were shooting from the other side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we went into a forest, and we found ourselves in such a situation, with the two armies shooting through.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And with my scouting experience, I knew that this was the worst situation we can be in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The forest could catch on fire, and we could just get killed, right when we smell the freedom.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
